.SH NAME
undefined \- undefined
.SH SYNOPSIS
The \f[B]\f[CB]undefined\f[B]\f[R] global property represents the
primitive value \f[CR]undefined\f[R].
It is one of JavaScript\(cqs primitive types.
.IP
.EX
\f[B]function\f[R] test(t) {
  \f[B]if\f[R] (t === \f[B]undefined\f[R]) {
    \f[B]return\f[R] \(dqUndefined value!\(dq;
  }
  \f[B]return\f[R] t;
}

\f[B]let\f[R] x;

console.log(test(x));
\f[I]// Expected output: \(dqUndefined value!\(dq\f[R]
.EE
.SH VALUE
The primitive value \f[CR]undefined\f[R].
.PP
